      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. DEL MAR JESSIE racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd in a NG on April 12 over 375m at this track behind Exit Mode beaten 3 lengths (21.77). Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including two wins, from four starts. Can find winning form. 8. TRIVIA goes very well this course and distance starting 16 times for eight wins and three minors. Comes off a (19.37) win last time, scoring by 8 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 342m at Angle Park. Looks suited here and can measure up. 4. VODKA SUNRISE finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her scintillating 21.44 win at this track over 375m. Should be in this for a long way. 7. EXIT MODE is in form and must include among the chances.\",\"runners\":[1,8,4,7],\"exclusive\":false}",
